  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Restoring the Social Contract-Improve Local Security &amp; Justice Systems</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Burundi and South Kivu (DRC) lack most basic services and providers for security and justice are often 
incompetent. The police is incapable of ensuring security and the justice system is weak, making access difficult.</narrative>
  </description>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">We aim to increase the performance of public administration, police and justice systems at local level and to 
restore the interaction between these state actors and society.</narrative>
  </description>
